Class DefineWarehousePointCommand

java.lang.Object
com.pld.agile.controller.DefineWarehousePointCommand
All Implemented Interfaces:
Command
public class DefineWarehousePointCommand extends Object implements Command
The DefineWarehousePointCommand class implements the Command interface and defines a warehouse point on a specific intersection. It allows for setting a warehouse in a delivery round and provides undo functionality to remove the warehouse.
